{
  "text": "Furthermore, deficits in executive functioning are widely reported in psychiatric populations including those affected by attention deficit/ hyperactivity disorder 1,2 (ADHD), autism spectrum disorder 1 (ASD), bipolar disorder 3 (BIP), major depressive disorder [CITATION_1] (MDD), schizophrenia [CITATION_2] (SCZ) and others. [CITATION_3] Whether factors associated with risk for",
  "correct_citation": {
